column5: We used Illumina short read sequencing followed by de novo assembly to build the transcriptome of Chlamydomonas acidophila, a green alga living in extreme habitats. The assembled transcripts were annotated functionally and classified in functional Gene Ontology groups. Transcriptomic expression was measured before and after Cd exposure in this and the model microalga Chlamydomonas reinhardtii from the same genus
column13: Comparison of genetic differences and transcriptomic response to cadmium between Chlamydomonas acidophila and Chlamydomonas reinhardtii
column14: strain is the same, methodology is the same, submission institution is the same
